-1.title: Hunting Mule Deer and Antelope in the West
-1.plot: Eastmans' family friend Fred Trueblood hunts mule deer and antelope in this sample of western fair chase hunting.

imdb.plot outline: Eastmans' Hunting TV is the only go-to source for do-it-yourself, fair chase, wilderness backcountry and western big game hunting. With over 60 years and three generations of experience, you'll be sure to gain the knowledge you need to successfully hunt trophy animals in the western United States. Join the Eastman family as they field judge and hunt across the West.
